      "reviews": [
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Flawless, Airbrushed Skin in Seconds \ud83d\ude0d\u2728",
          "reviewText": "I\u2019m seriously impressed with the QIUFSSE Air Brush Foundation! It glides on so smoothly, giving me that airbrushed, flawless finish without feeling heavy or cakey. \ud83d\ude4c The lightweight, moisturizing formula is perfect for all skin types \u2014 I\u2019ve tried it on mature skin and it still looks fresh and radiant. Coverage is buildable, so I can go natural for daytime or full glam for evening, and it blends effortlessly with my skin tone (02 Beige is spot-on for me!). Honestly, it feels like a little magic in a bottle \u2014 my makeup routine is so much faster, and my skin looks amazing every time. If you want smooth, radiant, camera-ready skin without the fuss, this foundation is a total must-have. \ud83d\udc96",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2025",
          "customer": "Amazon Customer",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AEEPWA3NVFKVBFAWYVUS7DH4JYIQ",
          "customerStarsRating": 5,
          "productSpecs": {
            "color": "02 Beige"
          },
          "helpfulVotes": "26 people found this helpful"
        },
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Wonderful product worth getting.",
          "reviewText": "Tried this out for the first time this morning. It was easy to put on. Comes with a makeup brush, two makeup pads and the can of Airbrush foundation. After reading the instructiions and watched a video on it I tried it. You apply the spray to the applicator (brush) then blend in on your face starting at the chin. I only did one application to see how it would feel and look. It gives a nice glow to the skin and coverage is good working it around. It does not feel heavy at all. Has a soft feel to my face when I touch it. I put blush on after and no pilling from doing that went on nicely. Some areas may need another sweep but for today just wanted to see how it would work for me. I'm 62 have some lines and this makeup did not bunch in the wrinkles I have around my mouth at all or under my eyes. I need to us under eye coverage for dark areas have to see if they have something for that. But at my age have to say this is a winner. Be careful when you spray cover the table with a paper towel only have to press lightly to spray it fans out.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on October 25, 2025",
          "customer": "MJL",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AH46NHQ2COI5GLUKADORGLMBUJ2Q",
          "customerStarsRating": 5,
          "productSpecs": {
            "color": "01 Natural/Warm Porcelain"
          },
          "helpfulVotes": "31 people found this helpful"
        },
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Nice foundation",
          "reviewText": "Can get blotchy if not careful",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on March 21, 2026",
          "customer": "Amazon Customer",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AGLUWEJWLYVKVFA4X7EIURGMQTWA",
          "customerStarsRating": 4,
          "productSpecs": {
            "color": "02 Beige"
          }
        },
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Beautiful finish, just watch out for overspray.",
          "reviewText": "I really love the results of this airbrush makeup foundation! The coverage is smooth, lightweight, and gives a flawless, professional-looking finish every time. It blends beautifully and feels much lighter than traditional foundation, which is a huge plus for all-day wear. The only thing to be aware of is the overspray\u2014it can drift onto nearby items if you\u2019re not careful. I\u2019ve learned to apply it in a more open space or use a small towel to protect the area. Overall, the finish and ease of application make it absolutely worth it. Gorgeous results with just a little extra caution. Highly recommend!",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on November 24, 2025",
          "customer": "Sandy C.",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AGOAEYLPBVBK33TCNWSQSIPCMGVA",
          "customerStarsRating": 5,
